{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ec3a9c03eb","title":"黄克诚梁兴初两部速至锦州充当歼灭顽军之主力","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"81c852e378","index":0,"year":1945,"month":11,"day":7,"articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"53b4258cee","name":"梁兴初","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b98ad668b2","type":"paragraph","text":"黄克诚梁兴初两部速至锦州","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"},{"id":"27ba81a6f4","type":"paragraph","text":"充当歼灭顽军之主力","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"},{"id":"9efd9792cb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年11月7日）富春、克读山海关发生战事，该处有李运自杨国夫-两部当可退带顽军前进，掩护黄梁两部到锦州。黄染任务是迅速到锦州充当轩灭顽军之主力，你们到玉由后立即调查由玉由通往锦州路线，不走山海关，走山海关以西，阴酸前进，以免暴露，看地图似以走喜峰口为宜。喜峰口、山海关中同地区是否有直路，请调查。路线确定后，处，与东北局彭林接头，解决两部各项问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"},{"id":"f1278dbdf7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"},{"id":"0ac81e99ae","type":"paragraph","text":"成膜1]富春，即李富春，原任中共中央副秘书长兼中央办公厅主任，此时正调赴东北。克诚，即黄克诚，当时任新四军第三师师长兼政治委员。[2]李运昌，当时任东北人民自治军第二副司令。杨国夫，当时任山东[3]黄，指黄克诚。梁，指梁兴初，当时任山东军区第一师师长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb"}],"page":{"id":"a4dc67eab4","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"ec3a9c03eb","start":70,"end":70}}}},"__N_SSG":true}